rs\", \"from\": 327, \"to\": 337}, {\"ngram\": \"the organizers\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 423}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The show's director weaklytried to arguethat it had nothing to do with \\\"The Last Supper\\\": The ceremony's artistic directorThomas Jollyhad distanced his scene from any \\\"Last Supper\\\" parallels after the ceremony, saying it was meant to celebrate diversity and pay tribute to feasting and French gastronomy.\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 754, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 736, \"end\": 742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9877777408979335, \"rank\": 0.01236846637695701, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The show's director\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 468}, {\"ngram\": \"arguethat\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 493}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 508}, {\"ngram\": \"The Last Supper\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 536}, {\"ngram\": \"The ceremony's artistic directorThomas\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 577}, {\"ngram\": \"Jollyhad\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 586}, {\"ngram\": \"his scene\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 606}, {\"ngram\": \"any \\\"Last Supper\\\" parallels\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 639}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 646, \"to\": 658}, {\"ngram\": \"diversity\", \"from\": 693, \"to\": 702}, {\"ngram\": \"tribute\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic organizers apologize to anyone who was offended during the opening ceremonies.\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 842, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic organizers\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 774}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 794}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremonies\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 841}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not really an apology though, it's just another tiring attempt to say it was about inclusivity.\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 943, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an apology\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 869}, {\"ngram\": \"just another tiring attempt\", \"from\": 883, \"to\": 910}, {\"ngram\": \"inclusivity\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 942}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not inclusive when you mock billions of people's religious beliefs.pic.twitter.com/xM305psf6y Organizers laughably claimed that it was \\\"clearly\\\" not meant to offend anyone, although, to many viewers, it was \\\"clearly\\\" intended to do just that.\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 1192, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"billions\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 985}, {\"ngram\": \"people's religious beliefs.pic.twitter.com/xM305psf6y Organizers\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1053}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1120}, {\"ngram\": \"many viewers\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1147}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Clearly there was never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group.\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1274, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an intention\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1231}, {\"ngram\": \"any religious group\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1273}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the contrary, I think (with) Thomas Jolly, we really did try to celebrate community tolerance,\\\" Descamps said.\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1388, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1374, \"end\": 1382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the contrary\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1290}, {\"ngram\": \"community tolerance\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1371}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Looking at the result of the polls that we shared, we believe that this ambition was achieved.\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1484, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": 